<paragraph blockId="29.[151,420,151,210]" box="[151,389,186,210]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
(
<figureCitation box="[159,243,186,210]" captionStart="FIGURE 26. M" captionStartId="29.[151,250,1965,1988]" captionTargetBox="[209,1377,790,1940]" captionTargetId="figure@29.[188,1398,767,1944]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="FIGURE 26. M. irisa sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: subgenital plate, ventral view; C: style, dorsal view; D &amp; E: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view; F: valve, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206141/files/figure.png" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
Fig. 
<number box="[212,243,186,210]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="26.0">26</number>
</figureCitation>
; Plate III: G)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="29.[151,1436,258,714]" box="[151,402,258,282]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Length. Male: 4.0mm.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="29.[151,1436,258,714]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Head and pronotum pale yellow; vertex with six small, dark brown marks on anterior margin, some yellow brown patches on vertex (Plate III: G); frontoclypeus with fuscous arcs. Pronotum with six yellow brown longitudinal stripes (Plate III: G). Leg marked with dark brown. Forewing light brown, cells bordered with dark brown, sometimes fuscous spots present at base of central subapical cell and claval area.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="29.[151,1436,258,714]" box="[197,857,438,462]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Forewing macropterous, inner anteapical cell open basally.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="29" pageNumber="30" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="29.[151,1436,258,714]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,378,474,499]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Subgenital plate short, subtriangular, lateral margin almost straight, apex acute (
<figureCitation box="[1316,1403,474,498]" captionStart="FIGURE 26. M" captionStartId="29.[151,250,1965,1988]" captionTargetBox="[209,1377,790,1940]" captionTargetId="figure@29.[188,1398,767,1944]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="FIGURE 26. M. irisa sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: subgenital plate, ventral view; C: style, dorsal view; D &amp; E: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view; F: valve, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206141/files/figure.png" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
Fig. 
<number box="[1372,1403,474,498]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="26.0">26</number>
</figureCitation>
B); style preapical lobe short and narrow, apophysis short and robust, tapered to acute apex over distal half, slightly laterally curved (
<figureCitation box="[313,396,546,570]" captionStart="FIGURE 26. M" captionStartId="29.[151,250,1965,1988]" captionTargetBox="[209,1377,790,1940]" captionTargetId="figure@29.[188,1398,767,1944]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="FIGURE 26. M. irisa sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: subgenital plate, ventral view; C: style, dorsal view; D &amp; E: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view; F: valve, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206141/files/figure.png" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
Fig. 
<number box="[365,396,546,570]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="26.0">26</number>
</figureCitation>
C); connective as long as aedeagus, aedeagal shaft in lateral view narrow, upturned hook-like apically (
<figureCitation box="[254,341,582,606]" captionStart="FIGURE 26. M" captionStartId="29.[151,250,1965,1988]" captionTargetBox="[209,1377,790,1940]" captionTargetId="figure@29.[188,1398,767,1944]" captionTargetPageId="29" captionText="FIGURE 26. M. irisa sp. nov. A: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B: subgenital plate, ventral view; C: style, dorsal view; D &amp; E: aedeagus and connective, dorsal and lateral view; F: valve, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/206141/files/figure.png" pageId="29" pageNumber="30">
Figs 
<number box="[311,341,582,606]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="26.0">26</number>
</figureCitation>
D, 
<number box="[373,403,582,606]" pageId="29" pageNumber="30" value="26.0">26</number>
E).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
